                                A Little Bit About Me</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="entry">
                            <p style="text-align: center">
                                <strong><span style="color: #ffff99">“The boundless possibility of trying out and the
                                    instant knowledge of the outcome that stimulates one for further analysis of a rationale
                                    in question”&nbsp; </span></strong>is what I find most fascinating about Computers.
                            </p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                Hi, My name is Aravinth, I am a Web & Graphic designer based
                                in New Delhi, India. My interest in Computers blossomed in my childhood itself.&nbsp;Also
                                &nbsp;I started designing and drawing&nbsp; from that time itself &nbsp;and most
                                of my design skills and knowledge are self taught .&nbsp; Since my father is an
                                Electricals and Electronics Engineer, i had &nbsp;a chance to know the computers
                                in that time where Computers were not commercially available in our country.&nbsp;
                                Right since the beginning, Computer is a subject that has fascinated me with its
                                power of applications.
                                <br />
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <%--end of A Little Bit About Me--%>
                        <%--start of My Background--%>
                        <div class="posttitle" id="My Background">
                            <h2>
                                My Background</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="entry">
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                Furthermore, I hail from a middle class family from Eastern Sri Lanka. &nbsp;After
                                the completion of my High School education from St.Methodist Central College, Batticaloa,
                                Sri lanka in 2001, I and my family had migrated to Chennai, Tamil Nadu, &nbsp;Southern
                                India where my most of the dreams were fulfilled.
                            </p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                To enhance my skills in Computer Based Designing, I had chosen "Arena Multimedia",
                                An Institute which trains students in various fields of Multimedia. Then that was
                                the place where I excelled in my skill by taking a course on "Multimedia Specialization
                                in Graphics and Animations".</p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                After the completion of my Higher Secondary schooling, I took up Bachelor’s Degree
                                in Electronics and Communication Engineering at SRM University Chennai, India. My
                                intense focus in my field of study coupled with the aid of the excellent environment
                                provided by my college of study and lectures by eminent personalities have rendered
                                me with a strong foundation of the concepts and the capacity to build on them.
                            </p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                As a student of Electronics and Communication Engineering, I took deep interest
                                in subjects like Electronics Circuits, Digital Communication, Digital Signal Processing,
                                Microprocessors, Computer Communication and Networks. As a result, I chose to do
                                my project work on “GSM Cell Phone Controlled Two axes Robot for detection of Fire,
                                Temperature and Metal”, the project was prototype developed to show that any circuitry
                                can be remotely controlled over a long terrestrial distance using GSM Technologies.
                            </p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                After my graduation I was recruited by TATA Consultancy Services (TCS) as an Assistant
                                System Engineer. TCS is a company of TATA Groups which is a giant in the Indian
                                industries. Typical Indian folks say that TATA manufactures products from safety
                                pin till heavy vehicles. TATA influenced all the verticals of business. TCS is the
                                firm which gives all kind of Technical Solutions to private companies and Governments
                                all over the world. During my service period I was working for the project of Bharat
                                Sanchar Nigam Ltd (BSNL) where I was experienced in Mobile Telecommunication Networks
                                and Technologies.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <%--end of My Background--%>
                        <%--start of present--%>
                        <div class="posttitle" id="Present">
                            <h2>
                                At Present</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="entry">
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                I am currently working with Academia Grandiosa Medicinae (AGM) as a Technical Administrator.
                                AGM is a Coaching center for Medical exams which has more than 40 class rooms all
                                over India. At this place My current role tasks me to manage the digital department
                                whilst being heavily involved in the Networking Systems and work on graphics, logos,
                                banners, interactive medias and building Web applications.</p>
                            <p style="text-align: justify">
                                And Also I'm doing freelanced designing of Logo, banners, Websites and Software
                                Development for various private companies.</p>
                        </div>
